  "title": "Implement fleet run log persistence and runs query commands",
  "agent_type": "developer",
  "description": "Create the versioned fleet run-log store with atomic rewrites, prefix resolution, query helpers, and `runs list` / `runs show` command support for both completed and in-progress records.",
